[section#over.match.copy
    [:en] Copy-initialization of class by user-defined conversion
    [:zh_CN] 通过用户定义的转换进行类的复制初始化
[%[:en] overloading[!resolution[!initialization]]
  [:zh_CN] 重载[!～决议[!初始化]] ]
]

[para]
[:en] Under the conditions specified in [#dcl.init], as part of a copy-initialization
of an object of class type, a user-defined conversion can be invoked to convert
an initializer expression to the type of the object being initialized.
[:zh_CN] 在 [#dcl.init] 中指定的条件下，作为类类型对象的复制初始化的一部分，
可以调用用户定义的转换以将初始化式表达式转换为所初始化的对象的类型。

[:en] Overload resolution is used to select the user-defined conversion to be invoked.
[:zh_CN] 使用重载决议来选择所要调用的用户定义的转换。

[begin:note]
[:en] The conversion performed for indirect binding to a reference to a possibly
cv-qualified class type is determined in terms of a corresponding non-reference
copy-initialization.
[:zh_CN] 将引用间接绑定到可能被 cv 限定的类类型中所实施的转换，被确定为与之对应的
非引用复制初始化。
[end:note]

[:en] Assuming that [=lq][=cv cv1] [`T][=rq] is the type of the object being
initialized, with [`T] a class type, the candidate functions are selected as follows:
[:zh_CN] 假定“[=cv cv1] [`T]”为所初始化的对象的类型，其中 [`T] 为类类型，其候选函数选择如下：

[list]
[item]
[:en] The non-explicit constructors ([#class.conv.ctor]) of [`T] are candidate functions.
[:zh_CN] [`T] 的非显式构造函数（[#class.conv.ctor]）是候选函数。

[item]
[:en] When the type of the initializer expression is a class type [=lq][=cv] [`S][=rq],
conversion functions are considered.
[:zh_CN] 当初始化式表达式的类型为类类型“[=cv] [`S]”时，考虑转换函数。

[:en] The permissible types for non-explicit conversion functions are [`T] and any
class derived from [`T].
[:zh_CN] 非显式转换函数的允许类型为 [`T] 和任何派生于 [`T] 的类型。

[:en] When initializing a temporary object ([#class.mem]) to be bound to the first
parameter of a constructor where the parameter is of type [=lq]reference to
[=cv cv2] [`T][=rq] and the constructor is called with a single argument in the
context of direct-initialization of an object of type [=lq][=cv cv3] [`T][=rq],
the permissible types for explicit conversion functions are the same; otherwise
there are none.
[:zh_CN] 当初始化用以绑定到构造函数的第一个形参的临时对象（[#class.mem]），而形参类型
为“[=cv cv2] [`T] 的引用”，且构造函数是在对类型“[=cv cv3] [`T]”的对象进行直接
初始化的语境中调用时，显式转换函数的允许类型与之相同；否则没有允许类型。

[:en] Those that are not hidden within [`S] and yield a type whose cv-unqualified
version is the same type as [`T] or is a derived class thereof are candidate functions.
[:zh_CN] 其中在 [`S] 之中未被隐藏，且所产生的类型的无 cv 限定版本与 [`T] 相同或为其
派生类，这样的转换函数是候选函数。

[:en] A call to a conversion function returning [=lq]reference to [`X][=rq] is a
glvalue of type [`X], and such a conversion function is therefore considered to
yield [`X] for this process of selecting candidate functions.
[:zh_CN] 对返回“[`X] 的引用”的转换函数的调用是 [`X] 类型的泛左值，并因此在选择
候选函数过程中被当作产生 [`X]。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] In both cases, the argument list has one argument, which is the
initializer expression.
[:zh_CN] 在两种情况下，实参列表都有一个实参，就是其初始化式表达式。

[begin:note]
[:en] This argument will be compared against the first parameter of the constructors
and against the object parameter of the conversion functions.
[:zh_CN] 此实参将与构造函数的第一个形参以及转换函数的对象形参进行比较。
[end:note]
